OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779210357
OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,FA student has died, and three others
OL,7,Fare being treated following an
OL,8,Foutbreak of meningitis in Reading.
OL,10,FThe cases have all been confirmed as
OL,11,Fmeningitis B (MenB), which was linked
OL,12,Fto a cluster of fatal cases in Kent
OL,13,Fearlier this year.
OL,15,FHowever, this outbreak is not same
OL,16,Fstrain of MenB that was seen in
OL,17,FCanterbury in March and in Dorset, and
OL,18,Fthe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,19,Fis currently carrying out further
OL,20,Ftesting.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
