OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,FThe student who died was a student at
OL,7,Fthe Henley College in Oxfordshire.
OL,9,FOther confirmed cases attended three
OL,10,Fschools in the Reading area.
OL,12,FWhich schools have confirmed cases of
OL,13,Fmeningitis?
OL,15,FSo far, the UKHSA says three schools
OL,16,Fhave pupils who have tested positive
OL,17,Ffor the disease.
OL,19,FOne of those is the Henley College,
OL,20,Fwhich offers A-levels and vocational
OL,21,Fcourses to teenagers in sixth form.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
