PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779210357
OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,FOther cases have been confirmed at
OL,7,FReading Blue Coat School, which is an
OL,8,Findependent school in the Sonning
OL,9,Farea. It teaches children and
OL,10,Fteenagers from ages 11 to 18.
OL,12,FAnother young person was a student at
OL,13,FHighdown School and Sixth Form Centre
OL,14,Fin the Emmer Green area.
OL,16,FAnd a primary school pupil was said to
OL,17,Fbe recovering well from the disease -
OL,18,Fwho attends Westwood Farm Junior
OL,19,FSchool in Tilehurst.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
