OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779210357
OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,FMatthew Pearce, Director of Public
OL,7,FHealth at Reading Borough Council,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our thoughts and deepest
OL,9,Fsympathies are with the family and
OL,10,Ffriends of the young person who has
OL,11,Fsadly died, and with the other two
OL,12,Fyoung people who are currently
OL,13,Freceiving treatment.
OL,15,F"Reading Borough Council is working
OL,16,Fclosely with the UK Health Security
OL,17,FAgency (UKHSA) and NHS partners
OL,18,Ffollowing these three cases of
OL,19,Fmeningitis B infection.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779210357
OL,3,CMeningitis outbreak: Which schools and
OL,4,Ccolleges are affected?
OL,6,F"It is completely understandable that
OL,7,Fparents, young people and the
OL,8,Fcommunity may be feeling anxious at
OL,9,Fthis time. We want to reassure
OL,10,Fresidents that the risk to the wider
OL,11,Fpublic remains low. Meningitis B does
OL,12,Fnot spread easily.
OL,14,F"Parents, carers and young people who
OL,15,Fwant to know more can visit the NHS
OL,16,Fwebsite. It is important to recognise
OL,17,Fthe signs and symptoms of meningitis,
OL,18,Fwhich can appear in any order and may
OL,19,Fnot all be present.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
